    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IDUN是北欧神话中青春女神的名字，我们故事正是从人类踏上这颗以她命名的星球开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是《IDUN - 阵线推进官》的免费序章，拥有完全独立肉鸽玩法。玩家将直面虫潮，生存是你唯一要考虑的策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的肉鸽策略玩法将收录在游戏本体中，游戏本体将包含剧情战役模式及完整的肉鸽玩法。在等待正式版推出之前，不妨抢先体验一下全新的游戏玩法吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版的《阵线推进官》是一款可以随时移动炮塔的即时战略+塔防游戏。我们的目标是在被敌人的大军包围前从星球上提取到足够的资源。在这里，一个关于扣人心弦的爱情、欺骗和死亡的故事正在等待着您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >品类繁多的炮塔、英雄以及武器均可配置在战场之中，任君差遣。做好准备迎接铺满屏幕的虫群吧！官方QQ群：756246752 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RTS与塔防的神奇化学反应，随时移动炮塔的战术游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/1377e160119bd7266cfa61322e5c3eaa.poster.avif?t=1737387265\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/1377e160119bd7266cfa61322e5c3eaa.webm?t=1737387265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/1377e160119bd7266cfa61322e5c3eaa.mp4?t=1737387265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突破传统塔防限制，部署、移动、防守和进攻，自由掌控战场局势。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的虫群寻路AI，让防守必须顾及四面八方之敌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/77ae58e94f31cdc90e95a37bec3478ed.poster.avif?t=1737387265\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/77ae58e94f31cdc90e95a37bec3478ed.webm?t=1737387265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/77ae58e94f31cdc90e95a37bec3478ed.mp4?t=1737387265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次击败敌人都会形成独特的地形障碍与破坏(如自然壕沟、洪流)，战斗场景瞬息万变，动态改变你的战术选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心所欲的游戏操控掌握</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/0021b636c125205fbf45baa2c1c1cf1c.poster.avif?t=1737387265\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/0021b636c125205fbf45baa2c1c1cf1c.webm?t=1737387265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116470/extras/0021b636c125205fbf45baa2c1c1cf1c.mp4?t=1737387265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《IDUN - 阵线推进官》无缝支持鼠标和键盘、游戏手柄和触摸屏，现在还针对 Steam Deck 进行了全面优化。利用视觉和操控方面的大量自定义选项，可完全根据自己的喜好定制完美的游戏体验。</p>",
